{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016fyhi2Z91vewA3eG53wDsQ","type":"tool_result","content":"# Askewly Design System Index\n\n## Primary Entry Point\n\n**Entry Protocol** — Start here\n- URL: `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/entry-protocol.md`\n- Purpose: \"what to fetch, in what order, per design task type\"\n\n## Core Documentation (Principles & Contracts)\n\n| Document | URL |\n|----------|-----|\n| Design Brief | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/design-brief.md` |\n| Principles | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/principles.md` |\n| Anti-patterns | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/anti-patterns.md` |\n| Style Signature | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/style-signature.md` |\n| Recipe Format | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/recipe-format.md` |\n| Agent Asset Model | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/agent-asset-model.md` |\n| Component Restyle | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/component-restyle.md` |\n| Absorption Criteria | `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/absorption-criteria.md` |\n\n## Tokens & Taxonomy\n\n- **Tokens JSON**: `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/tokens/askewly.tokens.json` (3-tier DTCG format)\n- **CSS Variables**: `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/tokens/tokens.css`\n- **Pattern Taxonomy**: `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/pattern-taxonomy.md` (7 surfaces, 57 groups)\n- **Groups Data**: `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/ui-vocabulary/groups.yml`\n\n## Knowledge Base\n\n- **Expressive Stack**: `https://ui.askewly.com/llms/knowledge/expressive-stack.md`\n\n## Recipe Collections (43 total, all draft status)\n\nOrganized by surface: application-ui (6), commerce (6), data-display (8), docs (4), feedback (2), forms (4), layout (2), marketing (5), navigation (5), overlays (4)\n\n[Full recipe URLs available on request]"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f1423542-66b2-4